        <li>
            <a href="https://icons8.com/icons" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">
            Icons8
            </a> - 免费高质量图标和插图资源
        </li>
        <li>
            <a href="https://mixkit.co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">
